roughness and the mound width.\nIn particular, the power index for the surface roughness and the mound width\ngrowth, created by the third order numerical scheme, is more accurate than\nthose produced by certain second order energy stable schemes in the existing\nliterature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Mar 2019 05:47:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-11"}
