only allow testing a specific\nform of the modified commutator that depends on the mean value of momentum. The\nelectro-mechanical oscillators to the contrary enable testing of any form of\ngeneralized uncertainty principle directly due to much higher stability and a\nhigher degree of control.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Mar 2019 10:03:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 23 Aug 2019 08:43:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-24"}
